## Interface: 20505
## Title: Super Swing Timer
## Notes: Melee, ranged, and current-target enemy swing timer for Classic and TBC. Includes Blizzard options panel support, a top Quick Controls section with Visibility and Key Colors columns, slimmer 15px main bars with a derived 8px OH bar, class-colored swing bars with opacity-aware color swatches, a Rogue latency-adjusted Sinister Strike end-window cue on the MH bar with a separate toggle and color swatch, a polished Rogue Slice and Dice duration bar directly above MH with Classic-safe helpful-aura parsing, a single 4px Rogue vertical energy-tick helper to the left of MH, a red-by-default enemy bar with an in-game toggle and color control, a Hunter Auto Shot cooldown line with configurable safe/late window colors, a dedicated Hunter Auto Shot / Multi-Shot cast bar with live Steady Shot / Aimed Shot no-clip feedback and a trailing latency slice, Anniversary-safe auto-repeat state gating so transient stop events do not clobber the ranged timer mid-cycle, a Warrior Shield Block duration bar above the MH stack with a configurable height slider and color swatch, a Warrior Slam cast bar above the MH bar with a live countdown label, a UnitAura-aware paladin seal twist red-zone and reseal marker line, color-coded shaman weave assist overlays with per-family toggles plus cast-following indicators and a red moving spark, an Enhancement Shaman Flame Shock target-duration bar above MH, adjustable bar border size and background tint, in-addon texture previews with dedicated spark and weave texture browsers, spark positioning synced to the actual status-bar fill with a 3px default width, a Shaman Lightning Shield / Water Shield 3-bar charge tracker to the left of the MH bar with configurable color and gap spacing, and a temporary Test Bars preview for moving frames.
